    "Table 4 shows the top 20 words for reappraisals in both groups.",
    "Compared to humans, GPT-4 vocabulary seems to be more sophisticated including words that might commonly be found in reappraisals (e.g., \"opportunity\", \"instead\", \"consider\").",
    "Interestingly, we found some of those words over all Studies 1, 2 and 4 despite their differences in the situations that were reappraised.",
    "were removed before the analysis.",
    "Compared to humans, GPT-4 appeared to rely on more sophisticated vocabulary."
